name: LoLLYLeGS pants for baby / toddler
description: LoLLYLeGS pants are seriously cool, seriously comfy pants for summer. Featuring an Alexander Henryfabric with a thin vertical stripe of red, dark blue, pink, black, orange, purple, light blue, green and yellow on a white and natural background they are made from 100% cotton. The elastic waist and wide leg cut means they are cool enough to wear in the heat of summer. The leg length provides a bit of cover up from the sun and some crawling protection for knees too. The roomy cut provides a bit of extra space in the rear if you're using MCNs (modern cloth nappies). And there's a cute little pocket on the rear too. And when the time comes....the elasticised waist makes it easy for your little one to slide pants up and down independently for toilet training. To see this style of pants on a toddler don't forget to check out our GaLLeRY. ALL PRICES ARE AUSTRALIAN DOLLARS.
